N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 177.13 - Resolution procedures

State Regulations

The director of the office of the ombudsman shall develop
procedures to ensure that issues, complaints and grievances are resolved in a
timely and efficient manner. Notes
